description: Orthologous groups from STRING/eggNOG hierarchical orthology at the Fungi level, with pre-computed gene trees from eggNOG v5.0
tree_method: eggNOG v5.0 pre-computed gene trees (species tree reconciliation + ML inference)
citations: Szklarczyk, D., et al. (2023). The STRING database in 2023. Nucleic Acids Research, 51(D1), D483-D489. https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gkac1000

Huerta-Cepas, J., et al. (2019). eggNOG 5.0: a hierarchical, functionally and phylogenetically annotated orthology resource. Nucleic Acids Research, 47(D1), D309-D314. https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gky1085
